26f5aa0b52184ad99","tid":1181340,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:36:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d1fcca422d87bb4d84f8398b8fc53857eca536d","tid":1181340,"uid":43428,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"當其他民主社會討論更點解決社會政治問題<br />\n華人社會仲係度討論應唔應該、可唔可以討論政治<br />\n好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7324571f36138b9f9ac03a7496355dd53630ce8b","tid":1181340,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"994da9631ebcbf23062786d65658a07914688d89","tid":1181340,"uid":25833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9bd8e2a0c47e35d8ccab0f64192a667f0d0b8529","tid":1181340,"uid":2020,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"541c28245ea1f7020797e18934afe8ae716dddc0","tid":1181340,"uid":25833,"like":4,"dislike":36,"score":-32,"quote":{"pid":"6e2c620a5d2f092b1514e5c8cf5ab3080faecd11","tid":1181340,"uid":60793,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T22:14:38.000Z","msg":"擦邊球事實係大陸人先會用<br />\n因為大陸好興乒乓 擦邊球唔係正式咁得分但都算啦當你得分 好中意用黎比喻現實一啲有風險 比較敏感但又唔係話唔得嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n希望香港人可以用返粵語或者正統中文"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T00:19:57.000Z","msg":"擦邊球最多係差小小得唔到分，或者好猛車邊既得分，形容件事啱啱好係容許範圍邊緣，或者佢走法律罅，但件事係合法<br />\n點會叫唔係正式得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如d女露波差小小露點，就打檫邊球<br />\n踩界，踩鋼線都相似，但唔完全一樣用法<br />\n<br />\n踩界係講件事係挑戰你既底線，啱與唔啱之間，可以話合法，又可以話唔合法<br />\n<br />\n踩鋼線就講緊做好危險，好高難度既事<br />\n<br />\n但跟番樓上原文，用踩界唔太合理，既然23條立左法，佢意思應該唔會係挑戰佢底線<br />\n<br />\n擦邊球反而真係最貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T01:57:16.000Z","msg":"講到似層層咁係到灌輸蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地咪踩緊界囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舉個例 黑社會成班聚埋一齊 佢地話自己朋友聚會 但警察覺得係聚集搞事 <br />\n咁咪就係你所講既擦邊球囉<br />\n正常香港人係講踩界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"我不嬲憎蝗語，但事實係唔貼切架啦，咁就係灌輸蝗語？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你要舉例子唔該用番原句啦<br />\n<br />\n原句：澳門廿三條已立法<br />\n最多打下擦邊球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個意思姐係佢唔可以講政治講到出哂面<br />\n<br />\n你可以講：佢好隱晦咁講政治<br />\n<br />\n澳門廿三條已立法<br />\n所以佢講政治都要講得好隱晦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個先係佢句野既原意，又唔用蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而唔係話：澳門廿三條已立法<br />\n所以佢地拍踩界既政治片？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成件事都唔啱邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n踩界根本就表達唔到呢個意思，唔係意思似就代表可以取代黎用架，夾硬用就係愛廣東話咩師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係就成句再重新組織過"}]}